member.param:
Can be one or more of the following options:


X or Y: the coordinates;

Button: Left (default), Middle, Right, X1 or X2;

Wheel: WheelUp, WheelDown, WheelLeft or WheelRight;

Count: number of times to send the click;

Down or Up: if omitted send a down click followed by an up release;

Relative: treat the coordinates as relative offsets from the current mouse position.

One of the following:


the word CSV to parse in comma seperated value format;

a sequence of characters to treat as delimiters;

blank to parse each character of the string.

One of the following digits, or blank to use the default:


1 (default) folders are not retrieved (only files);

1 all files and folders that match the wildcard pattern are retrieved;

2 only folders are retrieved (no files).
